      "citation_id": "[CITATION_1]",
      "span_text": "Chamsi-Pasha et al reported a 74-year-old female with dyspnea and fatigue 15 months following bioprosthetic MVR; transesophageal echocardiography (TEE) showed severe diffuse bioprosthetic mitral valve leaflet thickening with severely restricted motion, indicative of diffuse thrombosis, which was successfully treated with thrombolytics and anticoagulation."
